        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Jerusalem. \"Salem\" was probably a shortened form of the full and complete name, like \"Peer\" for \"Baalpeor,\" \"Maachah\" for \"Aram-Maa-chah,\" \"El Kuds\" for \"Beit-el-Kuds,\" and the like. (So Professor Cheyne.) \"Salem\" is the ",
